}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "UF-214C-ASAGA-0811" is silkscreened on the top of the board. :This device is presumed to be an [http://www.actionstar.net/usb2hub_uf214c.htm '''Action Star''' UF-214C].
This device is using a single '''Genesys Logic''' GL850 4-Port USB 2.0 HUB IC ("GL850", "AS-20031", "0504MK945-16") and an [http://www.datasheetcatalog.org/datasheet/agere/FW803-09-DB.pdf '''Agere''' FW803] ("AGERE", "FW803-09", "662344310", "05181", "V") '''IEEE 1394''' Three-Cable Transceiver/Arbiter IC.
